    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382580/extras/61c8efccdb5c7d063d718c27e97fff42.avif?t=1721017959\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382580/extras/7a84f72936ef35c95ec9fb334f634945.poster.avif?t=1721017959\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382580/extras/7a84f72936ef35c95ec9fb334f634945.webm?t=1721017959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382580/extras/7a84f72936ef35c95ec9fb334f634945.mp4?t=1721017959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《一个叫Paako的游戏》是一款像素风横板Meta游戏。游戏讲述了一个游戏专业研究生如何完成他的毕设项目：《一个叫Paako的游戏》。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382580/extras/b873c451ddd390dbc2efffd3f5c5c039.avif?t=1721017959\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382580/extras/be915b5d74ea6e4fa3028ca8bee7b5dc.poster.avif?t=1721017959\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382580/extras/be915b5d74ea6e4fa3028ca8bee7b5dc.webm?t=1721017959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382580/extras/be915b5d74ea6e4fa3028ca8bee7b5dc.mp4?t=1721017959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>质量可靠的二段跳和蹬墙跳（经典的总是好的）<br></li><li>一个钓鱼小游戏（猜到了）<br></li><li>看一场脱口秀（为啥？）<br></li><li>找一份工作（如果找得到的话）<br></li><li>聆听你的内心回声（我才没有这种东西）</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382580/extras/c9e59e1a5c770b70dddb9692cf3692b5.avif?t=1721017959\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382580/extras/0cbc5e7b5b048efa20a5b54b83ed9ca8.poster.avif?t=1721017959\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382580/extras/0cbc5e7b5b048efa20a5b54b83ed9ca8.webm?t=1721017959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382580/extras/0cbc5e7b5b048efa20a5b54b83ed9ca8.mp4?t=1721017959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《一个叫Paako的游戏》最初是南加利福尼亚大学（University of Southern California）的学生毕设项目，在学生团队Team Paako的协助下，由黄超然开发制作。欲了解更多信息，请访问USC Games的出版商页面。如果想了解更多关于全球排名第一的游戏专业USC Games的信息，请访问南加利福尼亚大学游戏项目网站。",
